<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id05144bae-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d" identifier="/us/usc/t19/s339"><num value="339">§ 339.</num><heading> Restriction on consular certificates</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">No consular officer of the United States shall grant a certificate for merchandise shipped from countries adjacent to the United States, which have passed a consulate after purchase for shipment.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id05144baf-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d">(R.S. § 2861.)</sourceCredit>
